    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> panko breadcrumbs </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-8 min or until golden, stirring frequently</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
