    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Zest your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>(try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Chop your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 3,
