            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>broccoli</strong> (save the rest for later!) to a <strong>food processor </strong>with the <strong>peeled garlic</strong>,<strong> flaked almonds</strong>, <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>basil </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later)</p><p>Tip: No food processor? Chop everything up as finely as you can and mix it together!</p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>zested</strong> <strong>lemon[s]</strong>, 2 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[5 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
